WEBVTT

00:05.539 --> 00:07.241
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:07.274 --> 00:08.842
Audra:
GAYLE HAS A THING FOR ME.

00:08.876 --> 00:10.377
THEY'RE DANGEROUS, ANDY.

00:10.410 --> 00:11.812
FORNICATORS!

00:11.845 --> 00:13.313
