HEY, FUCK YOU.

00:27.461 --> 00:28.662
[ LAUGHS ]

00:28.695 --> 00:30.831
[ GRUNTING ]

00:30.864 --> 00:32.266
HER NAME IS PILAR ZUAZO.

00:32.299 --> 00:35.169
