MY PUBLIC IMAGE.

00:35.202 --> 00:36.436
NO.
BECAUSE SHE OWNS YOU.

00:36.470 --> 00:38.005
THIS LITTLE MILK BALL
WAS A MISTAKE,

00:38.038 --> 00:39.273
MISTAKE THAT WOULD END
THE CAREER

00:39.306 --> 00:41.975
OF A VERY PROMISING
POLITICIAN.

00:42.009 --> 00:44.378
