AND YOU HIT MY KID.

00:50.384 --> 00:52.686
ESTEBAN NEEDS YOU AND THE BABY
FOR PHOTOS,

00:52.719 --> 00:57.391
BUT, UH, SILAS AND SHANE ‐‐
THEY ARE ‐‐ WHAT'S THE WORD?

00:57.424 --> 00:59.393
EXTRANEOUS.

01:01.128 --> 01:03.797
WE DON'T NEED THEM TO COMPLETE
OUR PRETTY PICTURES.

01:03.830 --> 01:08.202
YOU COME ANYWHERE NEAR MY
CHILDREN, I'LL KILL YOU MYSELF.

01:08.235 --> 01:10.337
YOU LOOK
STUNNING IN BLACK.

01:10.370 --> 01:12.973
THE PEOPLE
WILL BE VERY SYMPATHETIC

01:13.006 --> 01:14.541
TOWARD THE GRIEVING MOTHER

01:14.575 --> 01:19.680
WHO HAS JUST LOST HER BEAUTIFUL
CHILDREN IN A TRAGIC...

01:19.713 --> 01:20.948
CAR ACCIDENT?

01:20.981 --> 01:23.684
OR PERHAPS A...
PLANE CRASH.

01:23.717 --> 01:26.520
OR PERHAPS ‐‐
[ GASPS ]

01:26.553 --> 01:27.988
Shane:
A CROQUET MALLET?

01:28.021 --> 01:30.424
I COULDN'T FIND
A GOLF CLUB.

01:45.405 --> 01:50.777
♪♪ LA LA ♪♪

01:50.811 --> 01:52.546
[ SIGHS ]

01:52.579 --> 01:56.850
♪♪ LA LA ♪♪

01:56.884 --> 01:59.052
