HOW THE LIGHTS CHANGE COLOR.

01:59.086 --> 02:00.454
I WONDER
IF IT'S A SALTWATER POOL.

02:00.487 --> 02:02.756
IT DOESN'T STING YOUR EYES
AS MUCH AS CHLORINE.

02:05.058 --> 02:06.560
NOT THAT THAT'S
HER ISSUE.

02:11.865 --> 02:13.300
Nancy: SHANE?

02:13.333 --> 02:16.770
DON'T LET GO
OF THAT STICK...THING.

02:16.803 --> 02:18.138
IT'S CALLED A MALLET.

02:18.172 --> 02:19.406
OH.

02:19.439 --> 02:20.407
WE'RE ON CAMERA.

02:21.542 --> 02:22.509
WHAT?

02:22.543 --> 02:23.977
COULD BE BROKEN.

02:24.011 --> 02:26.180
UH, GIVE ME THE STICK.

02:28.815 --> 02:30.050
IT'S CALLED A MALLET.

02:30.083 --> 02:31.285
IT'S SHAPED LIKE A MALLET.

02:31.318 --> 02:33.487
MM.
FOR HITTING THINGS HARD.

02:33.520 --> 02:34.521
<i>MALLET.</i>

02:34.555 --> 02:37.791
YOU NEED TO SHUT
THE FUCK UP.
OW.

02:37.824 --> 02:38.792
OW.

02:38.825 --> 02:41.328
YOU'RE HURTING MY HAIR.

02:41.361 --> 02:44.031
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

02:46.667 --> 02:47.835
OW, OW.

02:47.868 --> 02:49.503
OW. OW.

02:51.205 --> 02:52.439
Silas: WHERE THE HELL
HAVE YOU BEEN?

02:52.472 --> 02:54.107
I COULD HAVE BEEN INSIDE
EATING MINI‐SLIDERS

02:54.141 --> 02:57.511
AND MAKING SMALL TALK
WITH THE KING OF NICARAGUA.

02:57.544 --> 02:59.680
NICARAGUA
IS A CONSTITUTIONAL DEMOCRACY.

02:59.713 --> 03:00.848
HEY, COULD WE GET GOING?

03:00.881 --> 03:02.549
I NEED TO GET HOME
AND FEED THE BABY.

03:02.583 --> 03:03.884
GRACIAS.

03:03.917 --> 03:06.887
NOW YOU'RE IN A HURRY,
BUT WHEN I'M WAITING...

03:06.920 --> 03:08.222
IS THAT SUCH A GOOD IDEA

03:08.255 --> 03:10.490
WHEN YOU'RE ON YOUR WAY HOME
TO BREAST‐FEED?

03:10.524 --> 03:11.959
HEY!

03:11.992 --> 03:14.461
YOU'RE UNDERAGE...

03:14.494 --> 03:15.963
THANKFULLY.

03:15.996 --> 03:17.130
I THINK I'VE EARNED IT.

03:17.164 --> 03:18.765
I THINK YOU'VE GONE OFF
THE DEEP END.

03:18.799 --> 03:20.300
HA. DEEP END.

03:20.334 --> 03:21.201
NO.

03:22.469 --> 03:23.937
WHAT'S GOING ON?

03:23.971 --> 03:25.372
WE'LL TALK ABOUT IT LATER.

03:25.405 --> 03:27.474
WHAT'D YOU DO?

03:27.508 --> 03:29.476
I PEGGED OUT.

03:32.379 --> 03:35.916
WHY CAN'T I GET A FUCKING
STRAIGHT ANSWER FROM YOU PEOPLE?

03:35.949 --> 03:42.256
I, UH...
DON'T HAVE WORDS.

03:42.289 --> 03:43.524
THAT BAD?

03:48.729 --> 03:51.765
♪♪ DUéRMETE, MI NIÑO ♪♪

03:51.798 --> 03:54.434
♪♪ DUéRMETE, MI SOL ♪♪

03:56.770 --> 03:58.272
HOW WAS YOUR PARTY?

03:58.305 --> 04:02.776
WELL, PACK UP YOU,
PACK UP BABY.

04:02.809 --> 04:04.578
WE NEED TO BE OUT OF HERE
IN FIVE.

04:04.611 --> 04:06.446
