04:06.480 --> 04:07.614
vQUé PASO?

04:07.648 --> 04:10.951
COSAS MUY, MUY MALO.

04:10.984 --> 04:12.786
UH, VáMONOS.

04:12.819 --> 04:14.288
AHORA. RáPIDO.

04:14.321 --> 04:17.858
WHY AM I FUCKING TALKING SPANISH
TO YOU?

04:17.891 --> 04:19.526
MAKE.

04:19.560 --> 04:21.461
GO. DO. NOW.

04:21.495 --> 04:23.497
BABY THINGS.

04:23.530 --> 04:24.831
WE'RE LEAVING.

04:24.865 --> 04:26.466
HEY.
YOU WAIT A MINUTE.

04:26.500 --> 04:27.601
I LIKE THIS ONE.

04:27.634 --> 04:30.604
WE BOTH HAVE
THAT FIERY LATIN THING GOING ON.

04:30.637 --> 04:34.441
AND YOU BETTER NOT LET ANYTHING
HAPPEN TO THIS BABY.

04:34.474 --> 04:35.509
YOU HEAR ME?

04:35.542 --> 04:36.777
GONNA DO MY BEST.

04:36.810 --> 04:38.679
CRAZY LADY.

04:38.712 --> 04:40.647
LET'S GO.
AIR HOCKEY.

04:40.681 --> 04:42.349
I'D LIKE TO GO
IN THE HOUSE.

04:42.382 --> 04:43.150
CHILL A MINUTE.

04:43.183 --> 04:44.985
IF YOU GO IN AND I GO IN

04:45.018 --> 04:46.987
AND MOM COMES OUT
AND WE'RE STILL INSIDE,

04:47.020 --> 04:48.589
SHE'S GONNA SHIT
A HEDGEHOG.

04:51.458 --> 04:53.026
1‐NOTHING.
GO.

04:53.060 --> 04:55.028
SHANE, WHAT THE FUCK HAPPENED
AT THE PARTY?

04:55.062 --> 04:57.331
I KILLED PILAR WITH
A CROQUET MALLET BY THE POOL.

04:58.932 --> 04:59.900
GOAL.

04:59.933 --> 05:01.535
SERIOUSLY.
WHAT HAPPENED?

05:01.568 --> 05:02.402
SERIOUSLY.

05:02.436 --> 05:04.805
I KILLED PILAR
WITH A CROQUET MALLET

05:04.838 --> 05:06.974
BY THE POOL.

05:07.007 --> 05:08.175
SHE WAS GONNA KILL US,
SO I POPPED THE BITCH

05:08.208 --> 05:10.344
RIGHT IN THE MELON.

05:10.377 --> 05:11.345
THWACK!

05:11.378 --> 05:12.379
SPLASH.

05:12.412 --> 05:13.514
DEAD.

05:15.115 --> 05:17.584
YOU GONNA SHOOT?

05:17.618 --> 05:19.553
3‐ZIP.

05:19.586 --> 05:20.687
YOU SUCK.

05:25.092 --> 05:26.293
YOU'RE SERIOUS.

05:26.326 --> 05:27.661
AS SERIOUS AS DAD'S
HEART ATTACK.

05:27.694 --> 05:30.831
NOW, IN GENERAL,
I DON'T LIKE USING THAT SIMILE

05:30.864 --> 05:34.401
BECAUSE SOME HEART ATTACKS
JUST AREN'T ALL THAT SERIOUS.

05:34.434 --> 05:37.738
I MEAN, YOU RECOVER,
REDUCE YOUR SALT AND FAT,

05:37.771 --> 05:40.841
DROP A FEW POUNDS,
AND LIFE GOES ON.

05:40.874 --> 05:44.077
BUT DAD'S ‐‐
DAD'S WAS SERIOUS.

05:44.111 --> 05:45.712
YOU KILLED SOMEONE?

05:45.746 --> 05:47.814
YEAH, BUT I'M FAMILY.

05:47.848 --> 05:52.452
I MEAN, YOU GOT TO STILL
INVITE ME TO SUPER BOWL PARTIES

05:52.486 --> 05:53.620
AND SHIT LIKE THAT.

05:55.389 --> 05:57.424
I ASSUME YOU'RE FORFEITING
THE GAME?

05:57.457 --> 05:58.892
HOLY SHIT, SHANE.

05:58.926 --> 06:00.961
I DEFENDED THE FAMILY.

06:00.994 --> 06:02.763
MOM'S LUCK
WAS RUNNING OUT.

06:02.796 --> 06:03.830
YOU CALLED IT.

06:03.864 --> 06:06.233
YOU'RE PS‐‐ YOU'RE PSYCHO.

06:06.266 --> 06:09.536
MOM SAID YOU STOOD AND PEED
ON HER LEG ONCE WHEN YOU WERE 3.

06:09.570 --> 06:10.704
THAT'S KIND OF FREAKY.

06:10.737 --> 06:13.106
HOW FUCKED UP ARE YOU

06:13.140 --> 06:16.043
THAT YOU THINK THAT MY
3‐YEAR‐OLD SQUIRT FOR ATTENTION

06:16.076 --> 06:18.779
IS THE SAME AS YOU MURDERING
A WOMAN WITH A CROQUET STICK?

06:18.812 --> 06:20.447
IT'S A MALLET!

06:20.480 --> 06:22.816
I'LL BE IN THE CAR.

06:22.850 --> 06:26.286
[ CAR DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

06:37.698 --> 06:39.266
HOW DID YOU DO THAT?

06:39.299 --> 06:41.768
I WORK FOR YOU.
I'M ALWAYS READY TO FLEE.

06:41.802 --> 06:43.537
YOU SHOULD
KNOW YOURSELF BETTER.

06:44.805 --> 06:49.443
WILL YOU CALL THE GOONS
AND TELL THEM

06:49.476 --> 06:53.247
WE ALL WENT TO THE MOVIES
OR SOMETHING

06:53.280 --> 06:55.849
SO THERE'S NO WEIRDNESS
AT THE GATE?

06:55.883 --> 06:57.951
YOU KNOW,
IN ‐‐ IN ESPAÑOL.

06:57.985 --> 06:59.086
UH‐HUH.

06:59.119 --> 07:01.989
OH, Sí, SEÑORA.
EN ESPAÑOL.

07:02.022 --> 07:03.223
WOULD YOU HAPPEN TO KNOW

07:03.257 --> 07:06.793
ANYWHERE ESTEBAN
HAS SOME CASH STASHED?

07:06.827 --> 07:09.296
IN HIS CLOSET
IN HIS BLACK POINTY BOOTS,

07:09.329 --> 07:13.367
IN THE LEFT POCKET OF HIS WINTER
COAT IN THE HALL CLOSET,

07:13.400 --> 07:17.037
AND HE HAS NICE JEWELRY
IN THE DRAWER IN HIS BATHROOM ‐‐

07:17.070 --> 07:18.805
CUFF LINKS, WATCHES.

07:18.839 --> 07:20.474
HAVE YOU BEEN CASING
MY HOUSE?

07:20.507 --> 07:21.742
I DON'T TOUCH NOTHING.

07:21.775 --> 07:23.477
I'M JUST A CURIOUS PERSON.

07:23.510 --> 07:24.978
GO, GO, GO, GO, GO!

07:28.448 --> 07:29.683
[ WHISTLES ]

07:29.716 --> 07:32.553
♪♪ LA LA ♪♪

07:35.689 --> 07:37.524
♪♪ LA ♪♪

07:37.558 --> 07:39.493
WHERE'S YOUR BROTHER?

07:39.526 --> 07:41.762
I'M HERE.

07:41.795 --> 07:45.232
I'M GUESSING WE'RE NOT ALL
HEADED TO THE POLICE STATION.

07:45.265 --> 07:46.900
SO GLAD YOU GUYS TALKED.

07:46.934 --> 07:47.868
GET IN.

07:47.901 --> 07:49.636
ARE WE COMING BACK HERE?

07:49.670 --> 07:50.671
PROBABLY NOT.

07:50.704 --> 07:51.872
"PROBABLY NOT."

07:51.905 --> 07:54.041
SO YOU GOT TO GO IN
AND GRAB ALL YOUR SHIT,

07:54.074 --> 07:56.543
BUT I HAD TO STAND OUT HERE
WITH MY DICK IN MY HAND

07:56.577 --> 07:58.745
AND LEAVE EVERYTHING BEHIND.

07:58.779 --> 07:59.947
IS THAT RIGHT?

07:59.980 --> 08:01.381
YEAH.

08:01.415 --> 08:02.749
SORRY.

08:02.783 --> 08:04.918
SO, SO, SO, SO SORRY.

08:04.952 --> 08:07.888
[ Straining ]
FOR ALL THE COUNTLESS TIMES

08:07.921 --> 08:12.226
I'VE LEFT YOU HOLDING YOUR DICK,
I AM SORRY.

08:12.259 --> 08:15.028
BUT NOW YOU HAVE THE HANDBOOK
FOR WHAT NOT TO DO.

08:15.062 --> 08:18.365
AND AS WE DRIVE
FAR AWAY FROM HERE,

08:18.398 --> 08:21.068
WE CAN TALK ABOUT THE MANY WAYS
IN WHICH I FAILED YOU

08:21.101 --> 08:23.003
OR WE CAN PLAY
LICENSE‐PLATE BINGO.

08:23.036 --> 08:26.306
I'LL LET YOU DECIDE.

08:26.340 --> 08:27.875
[ SIGHS ]

08:27.908 --> 08:29.743
MOVE OVER.
CLIMB OVER ME.

08:29.776 --> 08:32.880
I'M NOT SITTING ON THE HUMP.
MOVE OVER.
I'M ALREADY BUCKLED.

08:32.913 --> 08:35.182
WELL, UNBUCKLE
AND MOVE TO THE MIDDLE.

08:35.215 --> 08:36.950
YOU REALLY DON'T WANT
TO MESS WITH ME, YOU KNOW.

08:36.984 --> 08:38.418
MOVE OVER NOW!

08:38.452 --> 08:39.353
OW!

08:39.386 --> 08:41.555
WHAT IS IT WITH YOU
AND THE VIOLENCE?

08:41.588 --> 08:43.790
