"I'M A KILLER NOW" CARD.

08:43.824 --> 08:45.325
THAT IS UNACCEPTABLE.

08:45.359 --> 08:46.393
FINE.

08:46.426 --> 08:47.494
ARE YOU A KILLER?

08:47.528 --> 08:48.929
I DON'T LIKE LABELS.

08:48.962 --> 08:50.831
MAYBE I SHOULDN'T KNOW
ABOUT THIS.

08:50.864 --> 08:52.633
NO, YOU SHOULDN'T.
AND YOU DON'T.

08:52.666 --> 08:54.134
YOU KNOW NADA.

09:00.307 --> 09:02.976
SILAS, YOU DRIVE.
I THINK I'M DRUNK.

09:03.010 --> 09:04.077
[ SIGHS ]

09:04.111 --> 09:06.246
I'M BURIED.
YOU HAVE TO DIG ME OUT.

09:21.862 --> 09:22.829
[ SIGHS ]

09:22.863 --> 09:24.665
OKAY.
IS EVERYBODY BUCKLED?

09:24.698 --> 09:25.999
