GO.

09:26.033 --> 09:28.368
IF WE CRASH, ALL THIS CRAP
WILL CUSHION THE IMPACT.

09:28.402 --> 09:30.270
I'M NOT GOING
UNTIL EVERYONE'S BUCKLED.

09:30.304 --> 09:32.539
SOMEONE HAS TO BE A ROLE MODEL
AROUND HERE.

09:34.274 --> 09:38.412
I'D LIKE YOU TO DROP ME OFF
AT THE BUS STOP, POR FAVOR.

09:38.445 --> 09:39.847
UH, ME AND STEVIE.

09:39.880 --> 09:41.548
HOW DOES
ONE OUT OF TWO SOUND?

09:41.582 --> 09:43.016
I CAN'T TALK YOU INTO IT?

09:43.050 --> 09:44.284
I MAKE 'EM, I KEEP 'EM.

09:44.318 --> 09:46.520
MAYBE YOU SHOULD
REVISIT THAT CONCEPT.

09:46.553 --> 09:47.554
SHUT IT.

09:47.588 --> 09:48.989
Shane: ARE WE GONNA DRIVE
LIKE THIS ALL NIGHT?

09:49.022 --> 09:51.258
MY THIGHS ARE GOING NUMB.

09:52.860 --> 09:55.562
MM, NO.
NO, WE'RE NOT.

09:55.596 --> 09:57.664
SILAS, DRIVE TO REN MAR.

09:57.698 --> 09:59.466
