FEELING CRAMPED.

10:07.474 --> 10:09.443
iEY, GUEY!

10:22.322 --> 10:23.490
[ LAUGHTER ]

10:31.698 --> 10:36.303
NO. AY, Sí, Sí.
AQUí.

10:39.540 --> 10:40.440
AY, NO.

10:43.810 --> 10:45.212
CLARO, GUEY.

10:47.714 --> 10:48.782
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:48.815 --> 10:50.017
HEY.

10:51.218 --> 10:52.319
HEY!

10:57.524 --> 10:58.659
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:58.692 --> 11:00.093
OYE.

11:06.567 --> 11:07.601
[ LAUGHTER ]

11:09.203 --> 11:13.106
AAAAAHHH!
WHOO‐HOO‐HOO!

11:26.019 --> 11:27.654
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

11:28.856 --> 11:30.424
AAH!

11:30.457 --> 11:32.426
iSáCAME DE AQUí!

11:39.433 --> 11:41.635
ANDY: Oh, sst!
Nance, don't go in there.

11:41.668 --> 11:42.870
ANDY?

11:42.903 --> 11:44.204
Shh, shh, shh.

11:44.238 --> 11:46.707
[ SIGHS ]
I NEED THE KEYS TO YOUR VAN.

11:46.740 --> 11:48.141
I'M GOING AWA‐‐
Shh!

11:48.175 --> 11:49.877
Away.
You can keep the Prius.

11:49.910 --> 11:51.011
Audra is in there.

11:51.044 --> 11:53.046
And I'm really,
really in a hurry.

11:53.080 --> 11:54.748
I fled, Nancy.

11:54.781 --> 11:58.452
When it came time for me
to stand up and be a man,

11:58.485 --> 12:00.387
I abandoned my lady.

12:00.420 --> 12:03.223
Did you happen to abandon her
with your keys in your pocket?

12:03.257 --> 12:05.125
No.
She loves driving the van.

12:05.959 --> 12:07.327
I'm going in.

12:07.361 --> 12:10.998
An antiabortionist with a
crossbow is holding her hostage.

12:12.799 --> 12:13.901
Fuck!

12:13.934 --> 12:15.636
Andy,
I really need those keys!

12:15.669 --> 12:17.070
Aah!

12:17.104 --> 12:18.438
I don't know
what I'm doing.

12:18.472 --> 12:20.607
Does this mean I don't love her?
'Cause I d‐‐ I love her.

12:20.641 --> 12:22.276
But I ran.

12:22.309 --> 12:26.413
I left her alone
with armed wacko Christy man.

12:26.446 --> 12:27.981
I'm taking him out.

12:28.015 --> 12:28.982
That's what I
should be doing.

12:29.016 --> 12:30.217
So you do it.

12:30.250 --> 12:32.119
Why haven't I done it yet?
I don't fucking know.

12:32.152 --> 12:34.188
Do you have something I can
clock him with?

12:34.221 --> 12:38.392
Yeah, I have a‐a‐a bat
and a big broom

12:38.425 --> 12:39.493
and a lawn statue.

12:39.526 --> 12:41.195
Oh, shit.

12:41.228 --> 12:42.763
She's never
gonna forgive me.

12:42.796 --> 12:44.198
Can we just talk
for a minute?

12:44.231 --> 12:45.332
THEY'LL FINE IN THERE.

12:45.365 --> 12:46.333
HE'S READING HER BIBLE VERSES
OR SOMETHING.

12:46.366 --> 12:48.068
YEAH,
I DON'T HAVE TIME FOR THIS.

12:48.101 --> 12:50.671
YOU ARE SO SELFISH.

12:50.704 --> 12:52.105
I'M IN CRISIS.

12:52.139 --> 12:55.442
ANDY, MY CHILD MURDERED SOMEONE.
I HAVE TO LEAVE TOWN NOW.

12:56.543 --> 12:58.245
What?

12:58.278 --> 13:00.347
What happened?
Who did Shane kill?

13:00.380 --> 13:02.749
WHY DO YOU ASSUME
IT'S SHANE?

13:04.184 --> 13:06.653
YEAH, WELL, ANYWAY,
IT'S REALLY, REALLY BAD.

13:06.687 --> 13:08.322
OH, IT'S ESTEBAN.

13:08.355 --> 13:09.656
IT'S NOT ESTEBAN.
DID HE KILL ESTEBAN?

13:09.690 --> 13:11.191
I GOT TO SAY,
I'M NOT SHOCKED.
NOT ESTEBAN.

13:11.225 --> 13:12.359
HE DIDN'T KILL ESTEBAN.

13:12.392 --> 13:14.561
ARE YOU GOING IN THERE
OR AM I?

13:14.595 --> 13:15.863
WHY DO YOU ASSUME

13:15.896 --> 13:18.065
I'M JUST GONNA GIVE YOU
MY NEW VAN THAT I BOUGHT
FOR ME AND AUDRA

13:18.098 --> 13:20.434
AS A SIGN OF OUR LOVE
AND OUR FUTURE TOGETHER?

13:20.467 --> 13:21.502
YOU FLED.

13:21.535 --> 13:22.503
I FLED.

13:22.536 --> 13:23.637
LISTEN.

13:23.670 --> 13:25.205
I'LL DISTRACT,

13:25.239 --> 13:28.041
AND IN A GREAT ACT OF MACHISMO
AND DEVOTION,

13:28.075 --> 13:31.044
YOU'LL BASH THE GUY
AND RESCUE YOUR LADY

13:31.078 --> 13:34.181
AND THEN YOU'LL GIVE ME
THE KEYS TO YOUR VAN.

13:34.214 --> 13:35.349
EVERYTHING WILL BE OKAY,
OKAY?

13:35.382 --> 13:37.217
OKAY. LET'S GO.
HAVE YOU BEEN DRINKING?

13:37.251 --> 13:39.887
MY CHILD MURDERED SOMEONE.
FAIR ENOUGH.

13:39.920 --> 13:42.055
I ALWAYS DO THIS.
I MAKE EXCUSES.

13:42.089 --> 13:44.424
BUT HE IS FUNNY

13:44.458 --> 13:46.059
AND BONKERS IN BED.

13:46.093 --> 13:48.061
I REALLY DON'T NEED
TO HEAR THAT.

13:48.095 --> 13:49.897
WHY DO I KEEP
PICKING LOSERS?

13:49.930 --> 13:51.965
THAT GUY WHO DROVE THE MUSTANG
SEEMED NICE.

13:51.999 --> 13:53.834
HUGE MOTHER ISSUES.

13:53.867 --> 13:55.302
HAVE YOU BEEN STALKING ME
FOR THAT LONG?

13:55.335 --> 13:57.004
HE AND I BROKE UP
THREE YEARS AGO.

13:57.037 --> 13:59.740
LET ME SAVE YOU, AUDRA.
PLEASE.

13:59.773 --> 14:02.609
LET'S WASH THE BLOOD
OF THE UNBORN OFF OF YOUR HANDS

14:02.643 --> 14:04.478
AND LIVE TOGETHER
IN THE LIGHT OF THE LORD.

14:04.511 --> 14:07.681
WE'LL MAKE BABIES.
I HAVE A TRUST FUND.

14:07.714 --> 14:10.284
GAYLE, YOU'RE A RELIGIOUSLY
DELUSIONAL SCHIZOPHRENIC.

14:10.317 --> 14:12.286
YOU'RE
A GODLESS BABY‐MURDERER!

14:12.319 --> 14:17.858
BUT I'M WILLING TO WORK WITH YOU
BECAUSE I LOVE YOU.

14:17.891 --> 14:20.427
EXODUS, CHAPTER 21 ‐‐
ARE YOU TAKING
YOUR ANTIPSYCHOTICS?

14:20.460 --> 14:23.163
OFF AND ON.

14:23.197 --> 14:24.198
THEY MAKE ME FAT.

14:24.231 --> 14:26.333
Nancy: HEY, AUDRA.
IT'S NANCE.

14:26.366 --> 14:29.570
JUST WONDERING IF I COULD GET
A QUICK ABORTION.

14:29.603 --> 14:30.771
SIT.

14:30.804 --> 14:32.606
SITTING.

14:32.639 --> 14:34.241
OF COURSE HE CALLED YOU.

14:34.274 --> 14:35.909
I REALLY
WAS JUST STOPPING BY.

14:35.943 --> 14:37.578
CAN I GET
THE KEYS TO THE VAN?

14:37.611 --> 14:39.313
NO TALKING.
HYAH!

14:39.346 --> 14:40.480
HA!

14:40.514 --> 14:41.615
TAKE THAT!

14:41.648 --> 14:43.483
AAAAHHHH!

14:43.517 --> 14:44.384
OH! OKAY.

14:44.418 --> 14:45.185
OH, SHIT.

14:45.219 --> 14:47.521
I SHOULD SMITE YOU RIGHT NOW!

14:47.554 --> 14:49.489
YOU HEDONIST!

14:49.523 --> 14:51.425
SON OF SATAN!

14:51.458 --> 14:52.459
OH!

14:53.193 --> 14:55.762
UM, GET HIM OFF ME.

14:55.796 --> 14:56.797
HE'S HEAVY.

14:56.830 --> 14:58.599
I HOPE HE CRUSHES YOU.

14:58.632 --> 15:00.234
[ GROANS ]

15:00.267 --> 15:03.170
I THINK WE SPEND HALF
OUR LIVES WAITING ON MOM.

15:03.203 --> 15:04.338
SHE KEEPS PEOPLE WAITING.

15:04.371 --> 15:06.006
IT'S HER ANNOUNCEMENT
TO THE WORLD

15:06.039 --> 15:08.275
THAT HER TIME IS MORE IMPORTANT
THAN EVERYBODY ELSE'S.

15:08.308 --> 15:12.412
I'M NOT SURE IF IT'S PURE EGO
OR FALSE BRAVADO.

15:12.446 --> 15:14.414
YOU KNOW WHY I PEED
ON HER LEG?

15:14.448 --> 15:15.415
WHEN?

15:15.449 --> 15:16.650
LAST NIGHT.

15:16.683 --> 15:17.985
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

15:18.018 --> 15:19.319
WHEN I WAS 3.

15:19.353 --> 15:21.955
'CAUSE YOU HAD TO PEE
AND SHE WAS IGNORING YOU.

15:21.989 --> 15:22.990
YEAH.

15:23.023 --> 15:25.659
YEAH,
THAT WAS PRETTY MUCH IT.

15:25.692 --> 15:27.828
WHERE DO YOU THINK
WE'LL GO?

15:27.861 --> 15:31.598
[ SCOFFS ]
I HAVE NO IDEA.

15:37.738 --> 15:39.506
WHAT'S IT LIKE?

15:39.540 --> 15:40.507
WHAT?

15:40.541 --> 15:43.010
KILLING SOMEONE.

15:44.244 --> 15:46.113
DO YOU FEEL DIFFERENT?

15:46.146 --> 15:47.548
NO.

15:47.581 --> 15:49.383
DO YOU FEEL BAD?

15:49.416 --> 15:51.585
I DON'T KNOW.

15:51.618 --> 15:53.754
I DON'T FEEL BAD.

15:53.787 --> 15:55.355
AT LEAST NOT YET.

15:57.057 --> 16:00.427
YOU TELL ME IF THEY COME.
THE ‐‐ THE FEELINGS.

16:00.460 --> 16:02.496
SURE.

16:02.529 --> 16:04.531
[ SIGHS ]

16:06.233 --> 16:10.270
WHAT THE HELL DOES SHE HAVE
IN THESE FUCKING BAGS ANYWAY?

16:14.608 --> 16:15.909
THIS BRACELET'S TINY.

16:15.943 --> 16:18.278
ARE MOM'S WRISTS
REALLY THIS THIN?

16:18.312 --> 16:19.947
UH, NO.

16:19.980 --> 16:22.382
BUT MEXICAN DICK IS.

16:22.416 --> 16:24.518
OH.

16:24.551 --> 16:25.819
I CAME BACK.

16:25.853 --> 16:27.821
I CAME BACK ARMED.

16:27.855 --> 16:29.556
I WAS DEFENDING YOU.
I HAD TO RUN.

16:29.590 --> 16:32.326
IF ‐‐ IF ‐‐
IF HE HAD HAD US BOTH TIED UP

16:32.359 --> 16:34.862
WITH THE BOW AND ARROW THINGY
POINTED AT OUR HEADS ‐‐

16:34.895 --> 16:36.330
BULLSHIT.
YOU BAILED.

16:36.363 --> 16:39.233
AND THEN WHEN YOU CAME BACK
WITH MOMMY OVER THERE,

16:39.266 --> 16:40.767
SHE HAD TO SAVE
YOUR SORRY ASS.

16:40.801 --> 16:42.236
I REALLY WAS
JUST STOPPING BY.

16:42.269 --> 16:44.438
CAN I HAVE THE KEYS
TO THE VAN NOW?

16:44.471 --> 16:45.506
YOU'RE RIGHT, YEAH.

16:45.539 --> 16:46.807
OKAY, YOU'RE RIGHT.

16:46.840 --> 16:48.075
GOD. AAH!

16:48.108 --> 16:49.309
I FREAKED.
I PANICKED.

16:49.343 --> 16:51.378
I DON'T ‐‐
I DON'T KNOW WHAT HAPPENED.

16:51.411 --> 16:52.246
YEAH, WELL, I DO.

16:52.279 --> 16:54.081
I FUCKED UP AGAIN.
I LET YOU IN.

16:54.114 --> 16:56.250
BIG MISTAKE, CLEARLY.
NO.

16:56.283 --> 16:56.984
UM, KEYS.

16:57.017 --> 16:58.652
[ SIGHS ]

16:58.685 --> 17:00.554
OW.

17:00.587 --> 17:02.289
JESUS.

17:02.322 --> 17:03.290
CALM DOWN.

17:03.323 --> 17:05.259
I SAVED YOU.
HOW ABOUT A THANK YOU?

17:05.292 --> 17:07.160
HOW ABOUT A FUCK YOU,
BITCH?

17:07.194 --> 17:08.729
YOU CRAZY FUCKING BITCH.

17:08.762 --> 17:10.330
YOU'RE MARRIED.
YOU HAVE CHILDREN.

17:10.364 --> 17:11.565
WHY COULDN'T YOU STAY AWAY?

17:11.598 --> 17:13.300
YOU KEEP HIM AROUND
LIKE A LITTLE PUPPY DOG.

17:13.333 --> 17:14.301
YOU USE HIM.

17:14.334 --> 17:17.538
WELL, I SINCERELY HOPE YOU GUYS
WORK IT OUT,

17:17.571 --> 17:18.939
BUT I'VE GOT TO GO.

17:18.972 --> 17:20.474
TAKE HIM WITH YOU.

17:20.507 --> 17:21.408
NO, NO, NO.

17:21.441 --> 17:23.076
I'M NOT DRAGGING HIM
INTO MY SHIT ANYMORE.

17:23.110 --> 17:24.878
NOTHING
EVER STOPPED YOU BEFORE.

17:24.912 --> 17:26.180
YEAH, WELL,
THINGS HAVE TAKEN A TURN.

17:26.213 --> 17:27.748
YOU DON'T THINK
I CAN HANDLE IT?

17:27.781 --> 17:30.150
I THINK YOU SHOULD TRY TO WORK
THINGS OUT WITH YOUR FIANCéE.

17:30.184 --> 17:31.752
THERE'S NOTHING
TO WORK OUT.

17:31.785 --> 17:33.287
I MEAN, LOOK,
ALL HE WANTS TO DO

17:33.320 --> 17:34.788
IS FOLLOW YOU DOWN
YOUR NEXT CROOKED ROAD.

17:34.821 --> 17:35.822
IT'S OVER.

17:35.856 --> 17:37.524
AUDRA, DON'T.
PLEASE?

17:37.558 --> 17:39.626
LET HER GO, YOU PUTZ.

17:39.660 --> 17:41.995
YOU'RE NOT GOOD ENOUGH FOR HER
AND YOU KNOW IT.

17:42.029 --> 17:44.164
SHUT UP, NUTBALLS.

17:44.198 --> 17:45.766
ANDY'S WONDERFUL.

17:45.799 --> 17:48.001
HE'S LOYAL, SCRAPPY.

17:48.035 --> 17:51.004
HE'S FUNNY
AND GREAT WITH KIDS.

17:51.038 --> 17:55.242
HE'S RESOURCEFUL.

17:55.275 --> 17:57.277
YOU CAN COME IF YOU WANT.

17:57.311 --> 17:59.479
YOU HAVE TO KNOW
IT ISN'T THE HEALTHY CHOICE,

17:59.513 --> 18:01.915
BUT YOU CAN...COME.

18:01.949 --> 18:02.916
I'D LIKE YOU TO COME.

18:02.950 --> 18:04.151
YOU SHOULDN'T.

18:04.184 --> 18:05.552
DO YOU WANT TO COME?
COME ON.

18:05.586 --> 18:06.520
NO, I WANT TO STAY HERE

18:06.553 --> 18:09.590
AND START MY LIFE
WITH THIS WOMAN I LOVE.

18:09.623 --> 18:11.859
UM, THAT'S NOT REALLY
AN OPTION ANYMORE, ANDY.

18:11.892 --> 18:13.393
WE'RE NOT GONNA WORK OUT.

18:13.427 --> 18:15.495
[ SIGHS ]

18:16.830 --> 18:19.099
I REALLY HOPE
YOU CHANGE YOUR MIND.

18:19.132 --> 18:21.468
'CAUSE HE'S A GOOD GUY.

18:21.502 --> 18:22.636
HEY, THOSE ARE MINE!

18:22.669 --> 18:25.539
YEAH, THEY'RE MINE NOW.

18:25.572 --> 18:27.341
PROVERBS 12:22 ‐‐

18:27.374 --> 18:29.676
I DON'T ‐‐
I DON'T GIVE A SHIT.

18:29.710 --> 18:31.011
AND I'M STILL DRUNK.

18:31.044 --> 18:34.147
ANDY, MEET ME BY THE VAN
IF YOU WANT TO COME.

18:36.517 --> 18:39.219
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

18:39.253 --> 18:42.556
I'M NOT.
I'M STAYING HERE.

18:42.589 --> 18:44.791
SHE'S NOT CHANGING HER MIND.

18:44.825 --> 18:47.394
I'M NOT.

18:50.998 --> 18:53.500
SO I MIGHT AS WELL
JUST GO WITH NANCY.

18:53.534 --> 18:54.535
I KNEW IT!
WHAT?

18:54.568 --> 18:55.669
I FUCKING KNEW IT.

18:55.702 --> 18:56.904
"F." YOU FAILED.

18:56.937 --> 18:57.905
"F." YOU GET AN "F."

18:57.938 --> 18:59.206
YOU SAID
THERE WAS NO CHANCE!

18:59.239 --> 19:00.240
YOU WERE SUPPOSED
TO FIGHT FOR ME!

19:00.274 --> 19:02.609
AH!
GO AWAY.
JUST GO AWAY.

19:02.643 --> 19:05.012
YOU STUPID SON OF A WHORE.

19:05.045 --> 19:06.780
YOU HEARD HER!
GET OUT OF HERE!

19:06.813 --> 19:07.915
WHAT?!
THIS IS MY HOUSE!

19:07.948 --> 19:08.916
YOU GET OUT.

19:08.949 --> 19:10.217
I'M TIED TO THE CHAIR!

19:10.250 --> 19:11.985
AND YOU'LL STAY THAT WAY
UNTIL THE POLICE GET HERE.

19:12.019 --> 19:14.087
GAYLE, I AM FOND OF YOU,
BUT YOU NEED HELP.

19:14.121 --> 19:15.522
CHRIST'S LOVE
IS ALL THE HELP I NEED.

19:15.556 --> 19:18.292
YEAH, KEEP THINKING THAT.
IT'S SERVING YOU SO WELL.

19:18.325 --> 19:19.493
[ HORN HONKS ]

19:19.526 --> 19:21.094
[ SIGHS ]

19:21.128 --> 19:23.597
YOU SHOULD GO, ANDY.

19:24.498 --> 19:26.366
[ DIALING ]

19:26.400 --> 19:28.702
I REALLY DO LOVE YOU,
YOU KNOW.

19:30.571 --> 19:31.505
HELLO, POLICE?

19:31.538 --> 19:35.342
YES, I'M AT 124 ABALONE WAY
IN REN MAR.

19:35.375 --> 19:38.579
YES, A MAN BROKE IN
AND HELD ME HOSTAGE.

19:38.612 --> 19:40.314
THAT'S RIGHT.

19:40.347 --> 19:43.817
NO, I HAVE HIM TIED UP NOW.
I WAS ABLE TO SUBDUE HIM.

19:43.851 --> 19:45.219
NO, JUST ME.

19:45.252 --> 19:48.121
I HAVE A RESTRAINING ORDER
AGAINST HIM.

19:48.155 --> 19:51.425
THANK YOU.
I'LL STAY ON THE LINE.

19:51.458 --> 19:53.527
AUDRA?

19:56.563 --> 19:58.332
[ SIGHS ]

20:04.371 --> 20:04.872
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

20:04.905 --> 20:06.373
YES, STILL HOLDING.

20:15.949 --> 20:19.019
ANDY'S COMING?

20:19.052 --> 20:21.221
YEAH, SURE.
WHY NOT?

20:21.255 --> 20:23.857
NOTHING LEFT FOR ME HERE.

20:23.891 --> 20:26.760
I'M ALONE AGAIN, NATURALLY.
HA HA HA.

20:26.793 --> 20:27.828
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

20:27.861 --> 20:29.296
I BLEW IT.

20:29.329 --> 20:30.464
SHOCKER.

20:30.497 --> 20:32.499
SILAS, BE NICE.

20:32.533 --> 20:33.901
SORRY.

20:33.934 --> 20:35.836
SHE WAS CUTE.

20:35.869 --> 20:37.738
THANKS.

20:37.771 --> 20:39.206
I LIKED AUDRA.

20:39.239 --> 20:41.542
BUT YOU'LL GET OVER IT.

20:41.575 --> 20:43.610
TIME HEALS ALL WOUNDS.

20:43.644 --> 20:45.646
WELL, NOT ALL WOUNDS.

20:47.381 --> 20:50.484
I GUESS YOU HEARD.
YES, I KILLED SOMEBODY.

20:50.517 --> 20:51.919
ANY QUESTIONS?

20:51.952 --> 20:54.755
NO, I THINK I GOT IT.

20:54.788 --> 20:57.691
SO, UM...

20:57.724 --> 20:59.760
WHAT'S ALL THIS CRAP?

20:59.793 --> 21:01.461
IT'S ALL MOM'S.
NOT EVERYTHING.

21:01.495 --> 21:03.764
WE WEREN'T ALLOWED
TO GET OUR STUFF.

21:03.797 --> 21:05.432
I TOOK SOME OF YOUR THINGS,
OKAY?

21:05.465 --> 21:07.835
AND WE'LL GO SHOPPING.
IT'S JUST...STUFF.

21:07.868 --> 21:09.369
"JUST STUFF"?
OH, OKAY, THEN. FINE.

21:09.403 --> 21:11.605
HOW ABOUT WE LEAVE
SOME OF YOUR STUFF HERE

21:11.638 --> 21:12.506
BECAUSE IT'S "JUST STUFF"?

21:12.539 --> 21:14.274
HOW ABOUT
THIS LOVELY BAG OF SHOES?

21:14.308 --> 21:17.110
I'M AN ODD SIZE TO FIT.
JUST PUT THEM IN THE CAR.

21:17.144 --> 21:19.446
OKAY, WELL, THIS IS
GETTING A LITTLE RIDICULOUS.

21:19.479 --> 21:22.015
PLANNING ON PLAYING
A LITTLE CROQUET ON THE ROAD?

21:22.049 --> 21:24.518
THAT'S THE MURDER WEAPON.

21:25.519 --> 21:26.486
[ MALLET CLATTERS ]

21:28.288 --> 21:30.557
YOU KILLED SOMEONE
WITH A MALLET?

21:30.591 --> 21:31.758
THAT'S HARD‐CORE.

21:31.792 --> 21:33.894
SEE, ANDY KNOWS
WHAT IT'S CALLED.

21:33.927 --> 21:35.762
MAYBE WE SHOULD PUT IT UP
ON eBAY.

21:35.796 --> 21:37.431
"GENUINE MURDER WEAPON."

21:37.464 --> 21:40.267
WE'RE GONNA NEED THE MONEY
WITH ALL OF OUR SHOPPING.

21:42.469 --> 21:43.470
ANDY?

21:43.504 --> 21:44.972
WHAT?

21:45.005 --> 21:47.007
SO SORRY
TO DO THIS TO YOU.

21:47.040 --> 21:48.442
SILAS IS RIGHT ABOUT MONEY.

21:48.475 --> 21:50.210
YOU HAVE TO GO BACK
IN THAT HOUSE

21:50.244 --> 21:51.979
AND GET BUBBIE'S RING
BACK FROM AUDRA.

21:52.012 --> 21:54.181
WE MAY NEED IT.

21:54.214 --> 21:57.618
AND IT'S
YOUR BUBBIE'S RING.

22:00.020 --> 22:01.655
YOU'RE FUCKING KIDDING ME.

22:41.595 --> 22:42.763
RING?

22:42.796 --> 22:43.764
NO RING.

22:43.797 --> 22:44.898
JUST DRIVE.

22:44.932 --> 22:46.266
OKAY.

22:48.569 --> 22:50.404
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

